, "accession": "@GENE_SRSF1"}, "role2": {"identifier": "17127", "type": "Gene", "valid": true, "normalized": [17127], "database": "ncbi_gene", "normalized_id": 17127, "biotype": "gene", "name": "Smad3", "accession": "@GENE_SMAD3"}, "type": "Association"}, "nodes": [{"refid": "13", "role": "27,26"}]}], "pmid": 41271737, "pmcid": null, "meta": {}, "date": "2025-11-21T00:00:00Z", "journal": "Nat Commun", "authors": ["Liu Y", "Schüler SC", "Dumontier S", "Balg F", "Bedard S", "Desgeorges T", "Feige JN", "Boudreault PL", "Bentzinger CF"], "relations_display": [{"name": "associate|@DISEASE_Renal_Insufficiency|@GENE_SMAD3"}, {"name": "associate|@GENE_SRSF1|@GENE_FN1"}, {"name": "associate|@DISEASE_Renal_Insufficiency|@GENE_FN1"}, {"name": "positive_correlate|@GENE_SMAD3|@GENE_VAMP8"}, {"name": "associate|@DISEASE_Renal_Insufficiency|@GENE_VAMP8"}, {"name": "associate|@DISEASE_Renal_Insufficiency|@GENE_SRSF1"}, {"name": "positive_correlate|@GENE_FN1|@GENE_TGFB1"}, {"name": "associate|@GENE_SMAD3|@GENE_TGFB1"}, {"name": "associate|@DISEASE_Renal_Insufficiency|@GENE_TGFB1"}, {"name": "associate|@GENE_SRSF1|@GENE_TGFB1"}, {"name": "positive_correlate|@GENE_TGFB1|@GENE_VAMP8"}, {"name": "associate|@GENE_SRSF1|@GENE_VAMP8"}, {"name": "positive_correlate|@GENE_FN1|@GENE_SMAD3"}, {"name": "associate|@GENE_SRSF1|@GENE_SMAD3"}]}, {"_id": "41272451|None", "id": "41272451", "infons": {}, "passages": [{"infons": {"journal": "Mol Med;2025Nov21. doi:10.1186/s10020-025-01393-1", "year": "2025", "type": "title", "authors": "Aslam MR, Bilal M, Nawaz A, Kado T, Abe S, Phuong NQ, MemoonaKhalid S, Anh LD, Nishimura A, Watanabe Y, Igarashi Y, Iqbal N, Yokoyama M, Onogi Y, Hirabayashi K, Miwa H, Era T, Matzuk MM, Yamamoto S, Ikuta K, Usui I, Kobayashi K, Satake T, Kato M, Fujisaka S, Tobe K, "}, "offset": 0, "text": "Deletion of fibro-adipogenic progenitors-specific follistatin impairs muscle function and accelerates skeletal muscle atrophy in obese mice.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "4", "infons": {"identifier": "14313", "type": "Gene", "ncbi_homologene": "7324", "valid": true, "normalized": [14313], "database": "ncbi_gene", "normalized_id": 14313, "biotype": "gene", "name": "Fst", "accession": "@GENE_FST"}, "text": "follistatin", "locations": [{"offset": 50, "length": 11}]}, {"id": "5", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009133", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009133"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009133", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Muscular Atrophy", "accession": "@DISEASE_Muscular_Atrophy"}, "text": "muscle atrophy", "locations": [{"offset": 111, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "6", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009765", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009765"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009765", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Obesity", "accession": "@DISEASE_Obesity"}, "text": "obese", "locations": [{"offset": 129, "length": 5}]}, {"id": "7", "infons": {"identifier": "10090", "type": "Species", "valid": true, "normalized": [10090], "database": "ncbi_taxonomy", "normalized_id": 10090, "biotype": "species", "name": "10090", "accession": null}, "text": "mice", "locations": [{"offset": 135, "length": 4}]}], "relations": []}, {"infons": {"type": "abstract"}, "offset": 141, "text": "BACKGROUND: Follistatin is a potent regulator of various TGF-beta superfamily members, including myostatin (MSTN) and activin A. Previous studies have shown that follistatin is crucial in enhancing myogenesis during acute muscle injury. The mechanism by which fibro-adipogenic progenitors (FAPs)-specific follistatin influences muscle homeostasis in obese mice remains unknown. Therefore, we investigated the physiological role of follistatin in PDGFRalpha-positive FAPs in the regulation of muscle homeostasis and exercise in obese mice. METHODS: A PDGFRalpha-specific follistatin knockout (follistatin KO) mouse model was generated using PDGFRalpha-GFP-CreERT2 (PDGFRalpha-GCE) and follistatinflox/flox mice. These mice were fed a 60% high-fat diet (HFD) for 20 weeks, followed by a series of analyses, including exercise tolerance test, grip strength test, glucose and insulin tolerance assays, gene expression analysis, histology, western blotting, and immunohistochemistry. RESULTS: We showed that follistatin KO mice had reduced expression of Fst in skeletal muscle and white adipose tissue. We also showed that follistatin KO mice exhibited decreased exercise performance and altered skeletal homeostasis during obesity. Deletion of follistatin in FAPs activated the MSTN: Activin A/SMADs signaling pathways, which negatively impacted muscle homeostasis. Furthermore, follistatin KO mice showed reduced muscle mass, increased muscle degradation, and atrophic myofibers. Mitochondrial biogenesis, oxidative phosphorylation, and fatty acid oxidation were also altered in the skeletal muscles of follistatin KO mice. CONCLUSION: Follistatin plays a protective role in mice by maintaining the metabolic health of skeletal muscles; it restores muscle function during HFD challenge, thereby reducing diet-induced obesity-related complications.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "46", "infons": {"identifier": "14313", "type": "Gene", "ncbi_homologene": "7324", "valid": true, "normalized": [14313], "database": "ncbi_gene", "normalized_id": 14313, "biotype": "gene", "name": "Fst", "accession": "@GENE_FST"}, "text": "Follistatin", "locations": [{"offset": 153, "length": 11}]}, {"id": "47", "infons": {"identifier": "21803", "type": "Gene", "ncbi_homologene": "540", "valid": true, "normalized": [21803], "database": "ncbi_gene", "normalized_id": 21803, "biotype": "gene", "name": "Tgfb1", "accession": "@GENE_TGFB1"}, "text": "TGF-beta", "locations": [{"offset": 198, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "48", "infons": {"identifier": "17700", "type": "Gene", "ncbi_homologene": "3850", "valid": true, "normalized": [17700], "database": "ncbi_gene", "normalized_id": 17700, "biotype": "gene", "name": "Mstn", "accession": "@GENE_MSTN"}, "text": "myostatin", "locations": [{"offset": 238, "length": 9}]}, {"id": "49", "infons": {"identifier": "17700", "type": "Gene", "ncbi_homologene": "3850", "valid": true, "normalized": [17700], "database": "ncbi_gene", "normalized_id": 17700, "biotype": "gene", "name": "Mstn", "accession": "@GENE_MSTN"}, "text": "MSTN", "locations": [{"offset": 249, "length": 4}]}, {"id": "50", "infons": {"identifier": "14313", "type": "Gene", "ncbi_homologene": "7324", "valid": true, "normalized": [14313], "database": "ncbi_gene", "normalized_id": 14313, "biotype": "gene", "name": "Fst", "accession": "@GENE_FST"}, "text": "follistatin", "locations": [{"offset": 303, "length": 11}]}, {"id": "51", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009135", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009135"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009135", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Muscular Diseases", "accession": "@DISEASE_Muscular_Diseases"}, "text": "muscle injury", "locations": [{"offset": 363, "length": 13}]}, {"id": "52", "infons": {"identifier": "14313", "type": "Gene", "ncbi_homologene": "7324", "valid": true, "normalized": [14313], "database": "ncbi_gene", "normalized_id": 14313, "biotype": "gene", "name": "Fst", "accession": "@GENE_FST"}, "text": "follistatin", "locations": [{"offset": 446, "length": 11}]}, {"id": "53", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009765", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009765"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009765", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Obesity", "accession": "@DISEASE_Obesity"}, "text": "obese", "locations": [{"offset": 491, "length": 5}]}, {"id": "54", "infons": {"identifier": "10090", "type": "Species", "valid": true, "normalized": [10090], "database": "ncbi_taxonomy", "normalized_id": 10090, "biotype": "species", "name": "10090", "accession": null}, "text": "mice", "locations": [{"offset": 497, "length": 4}]}, {"id": "55", "infons": {"identifier": "14313", "type": "Gene", "ncbi_