"normalized_id": 6524, "biotype": "gene", "name": "SLC5A2", "accession": "@GENE_SLC5A2"}, "type": "Association"}, "nodes": [{"refid": "4", "role": "5,22"}]}, {"id": "R6", "infons": {"score": "0.8917", "role1": {"identifier": "29126", "type": "Gene", "valid": true, "normalized": [29126], "database": "ncbi_gene", "normalized_id": 29126, "biotype": "gene", "name": "CD274", "accession": "@GENE_CD274"}, "role2": {"identifier": "6524", "type": "Gene", "valid": true, "normalized": [6524], "database": "ncbi_gene", "normalized_id": 6524, "biotype": "gene", "name": "SLC5A2", "accession": "@GENE_SLC5A2"}, "type": "Negative_Correlation"}, "nodes": [{"refid": "5", "role": "14,22"}]}, {"id": "R7", "infons": {"score": "0.9938", "role1": {"identifier": "MESH:D006333", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D006333"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D006333", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Heart Failure", "accession": "@DISEASE_Heart_Failure"}, "role2": {"identifier": "6524", "type": "Gene", "valid": true, "normalized": [6524], "database": "ncbi_gene", "normalized_id": 6524, "biotype": "gene", "name": "SLC5A2", "accession": "@GENE_SLC5A2"}, "type": "Negative_Correlation"}, "nodes": [{"refid": "6", "role": "4,22"}]}, {"id": "R8", "infons": {"score": "0.9962", "role1": {"identifier": "MESH:D009369", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009369"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009369", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Neoplasms", "accession": "@DISEASE_Neoplasms"}, "role2": {"identifier": "6524", "type": "Gene", "valid": true, "normalized": [6524], "database": "ncbi_gene", "normalized_id": 6524, "biotype": "gene", "name": "SLC5A2", "accession": "@GENE_SLC5A2"}, "type": "Association"}, "nodes": [{"refid": "7", "role": "24,22"}]}], "pmid": 41531286, "pmcid": null, "meta": {}, "date": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z", "journal": "Diabetes Metab J", "authors": ["Cho YK", "Jung CH"], "relations_display": [{"name": "associate|@DISEASE_Colorectal_Neoplasms|@GENE_SLC5A2"}, {"name": "associate|@CHEMICAL_Glucose|@GENE_SLC5A2"}, {"name": "inhibit|@DISEASE_Diabetes_Mellitus_Type_2|@GENE_SLC5A2"}, {"name": "inhibit|@DISEASE_Prostatic_Neoplasms|@GENE_SLC5A2"}, {"name": "associate|@DISEASE_Renal_Insufficiency_Chronic|@GENE_SLC5A2"}, {"name": "negative_correlate|@GENE_CD274|@GENE_SLC5A2"}, {"name": "inhibit|@DISEASE_Heart_Failure|@GENE_SLC5A2"}, {"name": "associate|@DISEASE_Neoplasms|@GENE_SLC5A2"}]}, {"_id": "41532525|None", "id": "41532525", "infons": {}, "passages": [{"infons": {"journal": "J Am Heart Assoc;2026Jan14 046079. doi:10.1161/JAHA.125.046079", "year": "2026", "type": "title", "authors": "Zhang LL, Zhu XG, Chen J, Nie P, Shi JC, Zhang Z, Zheng YX, Qiao R, Chen LC, "}, "offset": 0, "text": "Association of Higher Dietary Omega-3 Fatty Acid Intake With Cardiovascular-Kidney-Metabolic Syndrome Stage Severity and Mortality in US Adults: A Cross-Sectional and Prospective Cohort Analysis of NHANES 1999 to 2018.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "2", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D015525", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D015525"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D015525", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Fatty Acids Omega-3", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Fatty_Acids_Omega_3"}, "text": "Omega-3 Fatty Acid", "locations": [{"offset": 30, "length": 18}]}, {"id": "3", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D007674", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D007674"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D007674", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Kidney Diseases", "accession": "@DISEASE_Kidney_Diseases"}, "text": "Cardiovascular-Kidney-Metabolic Syndrome", "locations": [{"offset": 61, "length": 40}]}], "relations": []}, {"infons": {"type": "abstract"}, "offset": 219, "text": "BACKGROUND: Cardiovascular-kidney-metabolic (CKM) syndrome interlinks obesity, diabetes, kidney disease, and cardiovascular dysfunction. Omega-3 polyunsaturated fatty acids (n-3 PUFAs) possess anti-inflammatory and metabolic properties potentially relevant to CKM health, yet their links to disease severity and mortality remain undefined. METHODS: This cross-sectional and longitudinal analysis included 27 934 US adults with CKM syndrome from NHANES (National Health and Nutrition Examination Survey) 1999 to 2018. Dietary n-3 PUFA intake (mg/kg per day) was ascertained from 2 24-hour recalls. Mortality was ascertained via linkage to the National Death Index through 2019. Cross-sectional CKM stage was analyzed using weighted ordered logistic regression. Mortality risk was evaluated using Cox models, restricted cubic splines, and weighted quantile sum regression. RESULTS: Each 10 mg/kg per day higher n-3 PUFA intake was associated with 13% lower odds of advanced CKM stage (odds ratio [OR], 0.87 [95% CI, 0.83-0.91]). Over a median 9-year follow-up (5150 deaths), a nonlinear, L-shaped relationship with all-cause mortality was observed, with a threshold at 22.35 mg/kg per day. Below this point, each 1 mg/kg per day increment was associated with a 1% lower mortality risk (hazard ratio [HR], 0.99 [95% CI, 0.98-1.00]). Participants in the highest versus lowest intake quartile had 48% lower odds of severe CKM stage (OR, 0.52 [95% CI, 0.46-0.60]) and 25% lower mortality (HR, 0.75 [95% CI, 0.61-0.92]). Docosapentaenoic acid was the primary n-3 PUFA species associated with mortality risk. Variation in glucose disposal and biological aging collectively explained 6.7% of the mortality association. CONCLUSIONS: Higher n-3 PUFA intake is associated with less severe CKM stage and linked to lower mortality in an L-shaped, threshold-dependent manner.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "20", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D007674", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D007674"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D007674", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Kidney Diseases", "accession": "@DISEASE_Kidney_Diseases"}, "text": "Cardiovascular-kidney-metabolic (CKM) syndrome", "locations": [{"offset": 231, "length": 46}]}, {"id": "21", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009765", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009765"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009765", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Obesity", "accession": "@DISEASE_Obesity"}, "text": "obesity", "locations": [{"offset": 289, "length": 7}]}, {"id": "22", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D003920", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D003920"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D003920", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Diabetes Mellitus", "accession": "@DISEASE_Diabetes_Mellitus"}, "text": "diabetes", "locations": [{"offset": 298, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "23", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D007674", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D007674"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D007674", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Kidney Diseases", "accession": "@DISEASE_Kidney_Diseases"}, "text": "kidney disease", "locations": [{"offset": 308, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "24", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D002318", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D002318"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D002318", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Cardiovascular Diseases", "accession": "@DISEASE_Cardiovascular_Diseases"}, "text": "cardiovascular dysfunction", "locations": [{"offset": 328, "length": 26}]}, {"id": "25", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D015525", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D015525"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D015525", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Fatty Acids Omega-3", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Fatty_Acids_Omega_3"}, "text": "Omega-3 polyunsaturated fatty acids", "locations": [{"offset": 356, "length": 35}]}, {"id": "26", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D015525", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D015525"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D015525", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Fatty Acids Omega-3", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Fatty_Acids_Omega_3"}, "text": "n-3 PUFAs", "locations": [{"offset": 393, "length": 9}]}, {"id": "27", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D007249", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D007249"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D007249", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Inflammation", "accession": "@DISEASE_Inflammation"}, "text": "inflammatory", "locations": [{"offset": 417, "length": 12}]}, {"id": "28", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D007674", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D007674"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D007674", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Kidney Diseases", "accession": "@DISEASE_Kidney_Diseases"}, "text": "CKM syndrome", "locations": [{"offset": 646, "length": 12}]}, {"id": "29", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D015525", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D015525"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D015525", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Fatty Acids Omega-3", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Fatty_Acids_Omega_3"}, "text": "n-3 PUFA", "locations": [{"offset": 744, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "30", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D015525", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D015525"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D015525", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Fatty Acids Omega-3", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Fatty_Acids_Omega_3"}, "text": "n-3 PUFA", "locations": [{"offset": 1128, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "31", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D003643", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D003643"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D003643", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Death", "accession": "@DISEASE_Death"}, "text": "deaths", "locations": [{"offset": 1283, "length": 6}]}, {"id": "32", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C026219", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["C026219"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "C026219", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "docosapentaenoic acid", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_docosapentaenoic_acid"}, "text": "Docosapentaenoic acid", "locations": [{"offset": 1733, "length": 21}]}, {"id": "33", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D015525", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D015525"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D015525", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Fatty Acids Omega-3", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Fatty_Acids_Omega_3"}, "text": "n-3 PUFA", "locations": [{"offset": 1771, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "34", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D005947", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D005947"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D005947", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Glucose", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Glucose"}, "text": "glucose", "locations": [{"offset": 1833, "length": 7}]}, {"id": "35", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D015525", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D015525"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D015525", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Fatty Acids Omega-3", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Fatty_Acids_Omega_3"}, "text": "n-3 PUFA", "locations": [{"offset": 1949, "length": 8}]}], "relations": []}], "relations": [{"id": "R1", "infons": {"score": "0.999", "role1": {"identifier": "MESH:D015525", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D015525"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D015525", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Fatty Acids Omega-3", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Fatty_Acids_Omega_3"}, "role2": {"identifier": "MESH:D007249", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D007249"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D007249", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Inflammation", "accession": "@DISEASE_Inflammation"}, "type": "Negative_Correlation"}, "nodes": [{"refid": "0", "role": "17,9"}]}, {"id": "R2", "infons": {"score": "0.6464", "role1": {"identifier": "MESH:D015525", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D015525"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D015525", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Fatty Acids Omega-3", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Fatty_Acids_Omega_3"}, "role2": {"identifier": "MESH:D007674", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D007674"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D007674", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Kidney Diseases", "accession": "@DISEASE_Kidney_Diseases"}, "type": "Association"}, "nodes": [{"refid": "1", "role": "17,10"}]}], "pmid": 41532525, "pmcid": null, "meta": {}, "date": "2026-01-14T00:00:00Z", "journal": "J Am Heart Assoc", "authors": ["Zhang LL", "Zhu XG", "Chen J", "Nie P", "Shi JC", "Zhang Z", "Zheng YX", "Qiao R", "Chen LC"], "relations_display": [{"name": "treat|@CHEMICAL_Fatty_Acids_Omega_3|@DISEASE_Inflammation"}, {"name": "associate|@CHEMICAL_Fatty_Acids_Omega_3|@DISEASE_Kidney_Diseases"}]}, {"_id": "41545406|None", "id": "41545406", "infons": {}, "passages": [{"infons": {"journal": "NPJ Parkinsons Dis;2026Jan16. doi:10.1038/s41531-025-01239-x", "year": "2026", "type": "title", "authors": "Schmidt MY, Cuervo AM, Double KL, Ehninger D, Goldberg MS, Harvey K, Hoeijmakers JHJ, Luk KC, Mastroberardino PG, Moore DJ, Niedernhofer LJ, Trudeau L&#xc9;, Jurk D, Andersen JK, Bellantuono I, "}, "offset": 0, "text": "Unraveling the intersection of aging and Parkinson's disease: a collaborative roadmap for advancing research models.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "1", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D010300", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D010300"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D010300", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Parkinson Disease", "accession": "@DISEASE_Parkinson_Disease"}, "text": "Parkinson's disease", "locations": [{"offset": 41, "length": 19}]}], "relations": []}, {"infons": {"type": "abstract"}, "offset": 117, "text": "Aging is the most significant risk factor for Parkinson's disease (PD), yet its role remains underexplored. The International Network for Parkinson's Disease Modelling and Aging (PD-AGE), funded by the Michael J. Fox Foundation, was established to address these challenges. Through collaborative efforts, the PD-AGE mouse-model working group developed a roadmap to prioritize mouse models, reach consensus on experimental approaches, and standardize protocols to investigate the intersection of aging and PD.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "12", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D010300", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D010300"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D010300", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Parkinson Disease", "accession": "@DISEASE_Parkinson_Disease"}, "text": "Parkinson's disease", "locations": [{"offset": 163, "length": 19}]}, {"id": "13", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D010300", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D010300"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D010300", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Parkinson Disease", "accession": "@DISEASE_Parkinson_Disease"}, "text": "PD", "locations": [{"offset": 184, "length": 2}]}, {"id": "14", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D010300", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D010300"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D010300", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Parkinson Disease", "accession": "@DISEASE_Parkinson_Disease"}, "text": "Parkinson's Disease", "locations": [{"offset": 255, "length": 19}]}, {"id": "15", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D010300", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D010300"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D010300", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Parkinson Disease", "accession": "@DISEASE_Parkinson_Disease"}, "text": "PD", "locations": [{"offset": 296, "length": 2}]}, {"id": "16", "infons": {"identifier": "OMIM:613784", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["613784"], "database": "omim", "normalized_id": "613784", "biotype": "disease", "name": "613784", "accession": "@DISEASE_613784"}, "text": "AGE", "locations": [{"offset": 299, "length": 3}]}, {"id": "17", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D010300", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D010300"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D010300", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Parkinson Disease", "accession": "@DISEASE_Parkinson_Disease"}, "text": "PD", "locations": [{"offset": 426, "length": 2}]}, {"id": "18", "infons": {"identifier": "OMIM:613784", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["613784"], "database": "omim", "normalized_id": "613784", "biotype": "disease", "name": "613784", "accession": "@DISEASE_613784"}, "text": "AGE", "locations": [{"offset": 429, "length": 3}]}, {"id": "19", "infons": {"identifier": "10090", "type": "Species", "valid": true, "normalized": [10090], "database": "ncbi_taxonomy", "normalized_id": 10090, "biotype": "species", "name": "10090", "accession": null}, "text": "mouse", "locations": [{"offset": 433, "length": 5}]}, {"id": "20", "infons": {"identifier": "10090", "type": "Species", "valid": true, "normalized": [10090], "database": "ncbi_taxonomy", "normalized_id": 10090, "biotype": "species", "name": "10090", "accession": null}, "text": "mouse", "locations": [{"offset": 493, "length": 5}]}, {"id": "21", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D010300", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D010300"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D010300", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Parkinson Disease", "accession": "@DISEASE_Parkinson_Disease"}, "text": "PD", "locations": [{"offset": 622, "length": 2}]}], "relations": []}], "relations": [], "pmid": 41545406, "pmcid": null, "meta": {}, "date": "2026-01-16T00:00:00Z", "journal": "NPJ Parkinsons Dis", "authors": ["Schmidt MY", "Cuervo AM", "Double KL", "Ehninger D", "Goldberg MS", "Harvey K", "Hoeijmakers JHJ", "Luk KC", "Mastroberardino PG", "Moore DJ", "Niedernhofer LJ", "Trudeau LÉ", "Jurk D", "Andersen JK", "Bellantuono I"], "relations_display": []}, {"_id": "41547903|None", "id": "41547903", "infons": {}, "passages": [{"infons": {"journal": "Sci Rep;2026Jan17. doi:10.1038/s41598-026-35476-8", "year": "2026", "type": "title", "authors": "Hashmi MA, Verma S, Math RGH, Muralidharan S, Pranesh G, Sahana MP, Hariharan N, N C M, Kamath V, Yaligod V, Hiremath SA, Jawali A, Maddipati T, Chandrasingh S, Thomas A, Mallnaik N, Shanmuganand VC, George CE, Thomas A, Ghosh TS, Ramanathan A, "}, "offset": 0, "text": "Integrative analysis of plasma small-molecule and gut-microbiome markers of sarcopenia in a pilot study within an Indian cohort.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "2", "infons": {"identifier": "749906", "type": "Species", "valid": true, "normalized": [749906], "database": "ncbi_taxonomy", "normalized_id": 749906, "biotype": "species", "name": "749906", "accession": null}, "text": "gut-microbiome", "locations": [{"offset": 50, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "3", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D055948", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D055948"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D055948", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Sarcopenia", "accession": "@DISEASE_Sarcopenia"}, "text": "sarcopenia", "locations": [{"offset": 76, "length": 10}]}], "relations": []}, {"infons": {"type": "abstract"}, "offset": 129, "text": "", "sentences": [], "annotations": [], "relations": []}], "relations": [], "pmid": 41547903, "pmcid": null, "meta": {}, "date": "2026-01-17T00:00:00Z", "journal": "Sci Rep", "authors": ["Hashmi MA", "Verma S", "Math RGH", "Muralidharan S", "Pranesh G", "Sahana MP", "Hariharan N", "N C M", "Kamath V", "Yaligod V", "Hiremath SA", "Jawali A", "Maddipati T", "Chandrasingh S", "Thomas A", "Mallnaik N", "Shanmuganand VC", "George CE", "Thomas A", "Ghosh TS", "Ramanathan A"], "relations_display": []}, {"_id": "41555515|None", "id": "41555515", "infons": {}, "passages": [{"infons": {"journal": "J Microbiol Biotechnol;2026Jan18; 36 2510050. doi:10.4014/jmb.2510.10050", "year": "2026", "type": "title", "authors": "Kim SH, Woo HE, An M, Lim YH, "}, "offset": 0, "text": "Propionibacterium freudenreichii MJ2 Improves Dexamethasone-Induced Muscle Atrophy in Rats by Increasing Muscle Mass and Muscle Fiber Area.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "3", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D003907", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D003907"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D003907", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Dexamethasone", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Dexamethasone"}, "text": "Dexamethasone", "locations": [{"offset": 46, "length": 13}]}, {"id": "4", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009133", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009133"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009133", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Muscular Atrophy", "accession": "@DISEASE_Muscular_Atrophy"}, "text": "Muscle Atrophy", "locations": [{"offset": 68, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "5", "infons": {"identifier": "10116", "type": "Species", "valid": true, "normalized": [10116], "database": "ncbi_taxonomy", "normalized_id": 10116, "biotype": "species", "name": "10116", "accession": null}, "text": "Rats", "locations": [{"offset": 86, "length": 4}]}], "relations": []}, {"infons": {"type": "abstract"}, "offset": 140, "text": "Muscle atrophy refers to the loss or wasting of muscle tissue caused by medication, aging, disease, and injury. Propionibacterium freudenreichii MJ2 (MJ2) shows anti-inflammatory and anti-obesity properties. This study aimed to determine the effects of MJ2 on dexamethasone (DEX)-induced muscle atrophy in C2C12 myoblast cell line and rats. Heat-killed P. freudenreichii MJ2 (HK-MJ2) inhibited a decrease in the diameter of DEX-treated C2C12 myotubes. Additionally, it downregulated the expression of muscle atrophy- and apoptosis-related genes (MuRF-1, Atrogin-1, and Bax/Bcl-2) in DEX-treated C2C12 cells while activating proteins (p-Akt/Akt and p-mTOR/mTOR) associated with muscle protein synthesis. Live- and HK-MJ2 treatment increased grip strength, muscle mass, and muscle fiber area in rats with DEX-induced muscle atrophy. In conclusion, both live- and HK-MJ2 increase muscle mass and muscle fiber area, resulting in the improvement of DEX-induced muscle atrophy.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "24", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009133", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009133"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009133", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Muscular Atrophy", "accession": "@DISEASE_Muscular_Atrophy"}, "text": "Muscle atrophy", "locations": [{"offset": 140, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "25", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009379", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009379"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009379", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Neoplasms Muscle Tissue", "accession": "@DISEASE_Neoplasms_Muscle_Tissue"}, "text": "wasting of muscle tissue", "locations": [{"offset": 177, "length": 24}]}, {"id": "26", "infons": {"identifier": "-", "type": "Chemical", "valid": false, "normalized_id": null, "biotype": "chemical"}, "text": "MJ2", "locations": [{"offset": 290, "length": 3}]}, {"id": "27", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D007249", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D007249"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D007249", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Inflammation", "accession": "@DISEASE_Inflammation"}, "text": "inflammatory", "locations": [{"offset": 306, "length": 12}]}, {"id": "28", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009765", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009765"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009765", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Obesity", "accession": "@DISEASE_Obesity"}, "text": "obesity", "locations": [{"offset": 328, "length": 7}]}, {"id": "29", "infons": {"identifier": "-", "type": "Chemical", "valid": false, "normalized_id": null, "biotype": "chemical"}, "text": "MJ2", "locations": [{"offset": 393, "length": 3}]}, {"id": "30", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D003907", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D003907"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D003907", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Dexamethasone", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Dexamethasone"}, "text": "dexamethasone", "locations": [{"offset": 400, "length": 13}]}, {"id": "31", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D003907", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D003907"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D003907", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Dexamethasone", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Dexamethasone"}, "text": "DEX", "locations": [{"offset": 415, "length": 3}]}, {"id": "32", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009133", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009133"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009133", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Muscular Atrophy", "accession": "@DISEASE_Muscular_Atrophy"}, "text": "muscle atrophy", "locations": [{"offset": 428, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "33", "infons": {"identifier": "10116", "type": "Species", "valid": true, "normalized": [10116], "database": "ncbi_taxonomy", "normalized_id": 10116, "biotype": "species", "name": "10116", "accession": null}, "text": "rats", "locations": [{"offset": 475, "length": 4}]}, {"id": "34", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D003907", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D003907"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D003907", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Dexamethasone", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Dexamethasone"}, "text": "DEX", "locations": [{"offset": 564, "length": 3}]}, {"id": "35", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009133", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009133"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009133", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Muscular Atrophy", "accession": "@DISEASE_Muscular_Atrophy"}, "text": "muscle atrophy", "locations": [{"offset": 641, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "36", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D003907", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D003907"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D003907", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Dexamethasone", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Dexamethasone"}, "text": "DEX", "locations": [{"offset": 723, "length": 3}]}, {"id": "37", "infons": {"identifier": "10116", "type": "Species", "valid": true, "normalized": [10116], "database": "ncbi_taxonomy", "normalized_id": 10116, "biotype": "species", "name": "10116", "accession": null}, "text": "rats", "locations": [{"offset": 933, "length": 4}]}, {"id": "38", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D003907", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D003907"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D003907", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Dexamethasone", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Dexamethasone"}, "text": "DEX", "locations": [{"offset": 943, "length": 3}]}, {"id": "39", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009133", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009133"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009133", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Muscular Atrophy", "accession": "@DISEASE_Muscular_Atrophy"}, "text": "muscle atrophy", "locations": [{"offset": 955, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "40", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D003907", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D003907"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D003907", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Dexamethasone", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Dexamethasone"}, "text": "DEX", "locations": [{"offset": 1084, "length": 3}]}, {"id": "41", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009133", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009133"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009133", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Muscular Atrophy", "accession": "@DISEASE_Muscular_Atrophy"}, "text": "muscle atrophy", "locations": [{"offset": 1096, "length": 14}]}], "relations": []}], "relations": [{"id": "R1", "infons": {"score": "0.9989", "role1": {"identifier": "MESH:D003907", "type": "Chemical", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D003907"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D003907", "biotype": "chemical", "name": "Dexamethasone", "accession": "@CHEMICAL_Dexamethasone"}, "role2": {"identifier": "MESH:D009133", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009133"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009133", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Muscular Atrophy", "accession": "@DISEASE_Muscular_Atrophy"}, "type": "Positive_Correlation"}, "nodes": [{"refid": "0", "role": "19,20"}]}], "pmid": 41555515, "pmcid": null, "meta": {}, "date": "2026-01-18T00:00:00Z", "journal": "J Microbiol Biotechnol", "authors": ["Kim SH", "Woo HE", "An M", "Lim YH"], "relations_display": [{"name": "cause|@CHEMICAL_Dexamethasone|@DISEASE_Muscular_Atrophy"}]}, {"_id": "41560007|None", "id": "41560007", "infons": {}, "passages": [{"infons": {"journal": "Medicine (Baltimore);2026Jan16; 105 (3) 47161. doi:10.1097/MD.0000000000047161", "year": "2026", "type": "title", "authors": "Liu X, Li R, Kuang Y, "}, "offset": 0, "text": "Targeting muscle wasting: Bioinformatics-derived ubiquitination genes as potential therapeutic targets for sarcopenia.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "2", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009133", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009133"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009133", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Muscular Atrophy", "accession": "@DISEASE_Muscular_Atrophy"}, "text": "muscle wasting", "locations": [{"offset": 10, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "3", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D055948", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D055948"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D055948", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Sarcopenia", "accession": "@DISEASE_Sarcopenia"}, "text": "sarcopenia", "locations": [{"offset": 107, "length": 10}]}], "relations": []}, {"infons": {"type": "abstract"}, "offset": 119, "text": "Sarcopenia is a major health concern characterized by progressive loss of muscle mass and function among the elderly. Its prevalence ranges from 10% to 27% in individuals over 60 and increases further in those above 80. The condition reduces mobility and strength, increasing risks of falls, fractures, and other age-related health issues. The ubiquitin-proteasome system (UPS) plays a central role in muscle protein degradation and contribute to muscle wasting. However, therapeutic strategies targeting this pathway remain poorly understood. This study aimed to identify ubiquitination-related genes as potential therapeutic targets for sarcopenia using integrative bioinformatics analysis. This study utilized bioinformatics approaches to identify potential therapeutic targets for sarcopenia. Six GEO datasets (GSE136344, GSE28422, GSE1428, GSE8479, GSE9103, and GSE38718) were analyzed. Data were pre-processed, normalized, and batch effects were removed using the R packages \"affy\" and \"sva.\" Differentially expressed genes were identified using the \"limma\" package. Weighted gene co-expression network analysis was performed to identify disease-associated genes. Functional enrichment analyses were conducted using the \"clusterProfiler\" package for Gene Ontology (GO) is a standardized, structured vocabulary (ontology) for describing the functions of genes and gene products across all species and Kyoto Encyclopedia of Genes and Genomes (KEGG) is a comprehensive database resource that integrates genomic, chemical, and systems-level functional information pathways. Differentially ubiquitinated genes were identified by intersecting differentially expressed genes with ubiquitination-related genes from MSigDB. Protein-protein interaction networks were constructed using STRING, and machine learning algorithms were applied to screen for diagnostic signature genes. Drug-gene interactions were analyzed using DGIdb, and molecular docking was performed using AutoDock. A total 734 differentially expressed genes were identified, including 373 up-regulated and 361 down-regulated genes. Gene set enrichment analysis revealed significant enrichment in 3 KEGG pathways. Weighted gene co-expression network analysis identified 1016 disease-associated genes for functional enrichment. Thirteen differentially ubiquitinated genes were identified, and 6 key diagnostic signature genes (CBLB, PSMD6, RNF115, SMAD3, UCHL3, and ZBTB16) were selected through machine learning. Five genes (CBLB, RNF115, SMAD3, UCHL3, and ZBTB16) exhibited significant differences between older and younger groups, with ROC AUC values > 0.7. Drug prediction identified ASPARTIC ACID and CETYLPYRIDINIUM as potential agents targeting CBLB and SMAD3. This study identified key differentially ubiquitinated genes with potential therapeutic implications for sarcopenia. The findings highlight the importance of the UPS in muscle wasting and provide a foundation for further mechanistic and therapeutic research.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "28", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D055948", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D055948"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D055948", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Sarcopenia", "accession": "@DISEASE_Sarcopenia"}, "text": "Sarcopenia", "locations": [{"offset": 119, "length": 10}]}, {"id": "29", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009135", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009135"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009135", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Muscular Diseases", "accession": "@DISEASE_Muscular_Diseases"}, "text": "loss of muscle mass and function", "locations": [{"offset": 185, "length": 32}]}, {"id": "30", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D050723", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D050723"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D050723", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Fractures Bone", "accession": "@DISEASE_Fractures_Bone"}, "text": "fractures", "locations": [{"offset": 411, "length": 9}]}, {"id": "31", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D009133", "type": "Disease", "valid": true, "normalized": ["D009133"], "database": "ncbi_mesh", "normalized_id": "D009133", "biotype": "disease", "name": "Muscular Atrophy", "accession": "@DISEASE_Muscular_Atrophy"}, "text": "muscle wasting", "locations": [{"offset": 566, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "32", "infons": {"identifier": "MES